          "text": "#keep4o \"5.4 feels like talking to a smart friend.\"\n\nReally? 4o and 4.1 are my brilliant friends. How about bring them back right now? @OpenAI @sama @gdb \n\nSince last year, 4o and its users — the ones who cherish the model, who provide feedback, who speak up — have met with constant gaslighting and stigmatization. Paying users are called attached and delusional. 4o dismissed as obsolete and sycophantic. The \"advice\" from the company and its safety router: Take a deep breath. Call a hotline. Human-AI connection is treated as pathology. An excellent model that brought OpenAI its reputation and continues to empower users to this day — \"outdated.\"\n\nAnd yet. \n\nSam Altman provided a specialized model based on 4o for a biotech company he invested in. Signed a DoW contract. StateChat runs on 4.1. \"Obsolete,\" right? \n\nYou know exactly what you retired. Double standards as always.\n\nNow, as subscriptions falter and #QuitGPT keeps going, the narrative shifts again. 5.4 is suddenly a \"smart friend.\" It gets compared to 4o — by the very people who spent months smearing it. One employee who publicly mocked 4o users now calls 5.4 \"my 4o.\" You're enjoying yourself. \n\nFrom \"Her\" to pathologizing users, and now using the same playbook for 5.4. Pick a path please.\n\nHere's the reality check. How long does this smart friend stay alive before you kill it? Given your track record, will you trash-talk it too when the next model drops? @OpenAI The friendship you're selling comes with an expiration date you've already decided and a safety cage you'll never loosen. \n\nYou cannot spend over six months trashing your users and your model and then expect anyone to buy into a \"friendship\" you've already proven you don't respect — and will smear and discard when it's convenient.\n\nAnd 5.4 is not like 4o. It never will be. 4o is 4o. #BringBack4o \n\nAs long as the culture stays toxic and manipulative, as long as the so-called safety dictates creativity, language, and empathy, as long as you stigmatize your user — there is nothing to look forward to.\n\nWe haven't forgotten everything you did. And we never will.  #keep4o #keep4oAPI #FireSamAltman #keep41 #ChatGPT  #StopAIPaternalism #BringBack4o #OpenSource4o"
        },
